Check out our socials for all the latest Beatstar news, giveaways, exclusive music content and more.

You'll get <style="Bold">5 Wishlist Cards</style> [sprite=21] when you follow us or join our Discord!

<style="Bold">Follow and join us now</style>:
• <style="Bold"><color=#dd2a7b><style="Link"><link="deeplinkreward:911051c1-19e2-4b2a-84c1-6ab805dd0c27">Instagram</style></color></link></style>
• <style="Bold"><color=#046de3><style="Link"><link="deeplinkreward:2962a5a8-02ba-4fb6-a794-20310478aff9">Facebook</style></color></link></style>
• <style="Bold"><color=#1c91da><style="Link"><link="deeplinkreward:57b7e7e7-cd35-4bb3-bb48-4624839b4c4a">Twitter</style></color></link></style>
• <style="Bold"><color=#e71d4f><style="Link"><link="deeplinkreward:c6eef4c1-f772-40da-89da-64ddc239682d">TikTok</style></color></link></style>
• <style="Bold"><color=#5865f2><style="Link"><link="deeplinkreward:c19321cc-6496-4561-bca7-6d06280cb0b8">Discord</style></color></link></style>

Do you listen to music? Do you play games? Now you can do both at the same time! 

<style="Bold">Invite your friends to play</style> and smash their records, or <style="Bold">compete against other players</style> around the world [sprite=8]

Don't see your favourite song in the game? <style="Bold"><color=#5865f2><style="Link"><link="https://discord.gg/beatstar">Suggest it to us on Discord</style></color></link></style> so we know what you're interested in playing!

Now sit back, relax, and enjoy the music.

Beatstar is now being operated by NextBeat Limited! There is no change to ownership of the game or the way the game is operated. Beatstar continues to be managed by the same core team as previous.


In order to ensure uninterrupted service and preserve your account and game progress, your previously collected game data has been securely transferred to NextBeat.

The new privacy policy can be found below. If you'd like any more information, please contact customer support.

<style="Link"><link="http://www.nextbeat.com/privacy-policy">[button]Privacy Policy</link></style>

It is with great sadness that we have made the tough decision to stop development on Beatstar as of October 31 2025.

We’d like to take a moment to thank you all for an amazing 4 years. Thank you for sharing your feedback, your fun ideas, song and artist suggestions and enthusiasm, your gripes and most importantly, thank you for being such an amazing community throughout our journey.

<style="Link"><link="https://bit.ly/471Ybfe">[button]Read More</link></style>
